com.cboe.interfaces.domain.product
Interface ProductClass

All Superinterfaces:
com.cboe.interfaces.domain.DomainBase
public interface ProductClass
extends com.cboe.interfaces.domain.DomainBase

A collection of products of the same product type. All derivative products of a product class have a common underlying product.
